		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;246&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;590px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;带着孩子们悠然走近，棕黄的沙滩上，模糊地可以看到一艘船的残骸隐匿在沙中。露出沙面的部分已然斑驳腐朽，唯一清晰可见的是船头的高耸形态，坚韧地诉说着这艘商船的历史。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://jumboalex.github.io/p/%E6%84%9F%E6%81%A9%E8%8A%82%E4%BF%84%E5%8B%92%E5%86%88%E6%B8%B8%E8%AE%B0/wreck1.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1022&#34;
	height=&#34;713&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://jumboalex.github.io/p/%E6%84%9F%E6%81%A9%E8%8A%82%E4%BF%84%E5%8B%92%E5%86%88%E6%B8%B8%E8%AE%B0/wreck1_hub85d4ec182db51da5aea3fc70bd12a8d_632859_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://jumboalex.github.io/p/%E6%84%9F%E6%81%A9%E8%8A%82%E4%BF%84%E5%8B%92%E5%86%88%E6%B8%B8%E8%AE%B0/wreck1_hub85d4ec182db51da5aea3fc70bd12a8d_632859_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
